"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-marathon-runner-elroy-gelant-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport ByWesley Botton Chief sports journalist 3 minute read 8 July 2024 11:21 am Elroy Gelant will compete at his third Olympics in Paris next month.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999987973447289, \"rank\": 1.2026567731684833e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3 minute\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"Elroy Gelant\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"his third Olympics\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 133}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Grant Pitcher/Gallo Images Elroy Gelant dreams of returning home with an Olympic medal, but the experienced distance runner is not getting ahead of himself in the build-up to the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"Grant Pitcher/Gallo Images Elroy Gelant dreams\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"the experienced distance runner\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gelant, a former national 5 000m record holder on the track, has had an awesome season on the road.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gelant\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"a former national 5 000m record holder\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"an awesome season\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He set a marathon personal best of 2:08:56 in Seville in February and went on to win the national title in 2:09:32 in Durban in April, which was enough tosecure a spot in the men's 42.2km raceat the Olympics, where he will turn out alongside compatriotStephen Mokoka.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999984647379695, \"rank\": 1.5321082432168386e-06, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 0.9999999999583906, \"rank\": 4.156380482711275e-11, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a marathon\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the national title\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 42.2km raceat\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"compatriotStephen\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old athlete also won the SA half-marathon title in Gqeberha last month, clocking 1:03:54 in cold and wet conditions, and he showcased his form again over the weekend bysetting a 10km personal bestof 27:47 at the Absa Run Your City race in Durban.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999997933173, \"rank\": 1.1316968673484235e-10, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gqeberha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 0.9999999999583906, \"rank\": 4.156380482711275e-11, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 37-year-old athlete\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"cold and wet conditions\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"his form\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10km personal bestof\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"the Absa\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"Your City race\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He credits the efforts of his coach, Jean Verster, and their training group in Potchefstroom for helping him find the best form of his career.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"score\": 0.9999998616569978, \"rank\": 1.3834302022538414e-07, \"text\": \"Potchefstroom\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the efforts\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"Jean Verster\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"their training group\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the best form\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winter in Potchefstroom is really cold, but even if it's minus two degrees, every morning at 4.45am we are out,\\\" Gelant said.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"score\": 0.9999998616569978, \"rank\": 1.3834302022538414e-07, \"text\": \"Potchefstroom\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Winter\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"two degrees\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"4.45am\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"Gelant\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not miss one day, even if we are sick, and I think that discipline and consistency has helped with my performances this year.\\\"\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"discipline\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"my performances\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gelant will compete at his third successive Olympics in the French capital, after finishing 13th in the 5 000m final at the Rio 2016 Games and taking 33rd place in the marathon in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8868296624245339, \"rank\": 0.12201437773187668, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9887481868850944, \"rank\": 0.011279713062483846, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gelant\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"his third successive Olympics\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5 000m\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rio 2016 Games\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"33rd place\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And though he wants a medal in Paris, he says a top-15 finish will be sufficient in terms of his personal goals.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999987973447289, \"rank\": 1.2026567731684833e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"a top-15 finish\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"his personal goals\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I train in the mornings I think of a medal, and everything I do, I am thinking of a medal, but I need to be realistic,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \